  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "Since STATICCALL enforces that no change can be made to state, it seems that the snapshotting of state in [here](https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/blob/master/core/vm/evm.go#L344) and subsequent `revertToSnapshot` is redundant. \r\n\r\nIndeed, I tried commenting out L344 and L362 and I'm still passing the tests in `GeneralStateTests/stStaticCall`.\r\n\r\nIs there any other reason that it is included that I have missed? It might be a simple copy-paste mistake.",
